ActIndian Act
SubjectSnuneymuxw First Nation 79 Acre Reserve Settlement Agreement
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to execute, on behalf of Her Majesty in right of Canada, the Snuneymuxw First Nation 79 Acre Reserve SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between Canada and the SNUNEYMUXW FIRST NATION; and (2) accepting the absolute surrender of lands, pursuant to sections 38, 39 and 40 of the Indian Act.
